An aged Facebook Page hands you something a new Page cannot buy: history. Real activity over time creates trust signals that help your Page perform smoothly from day one, while a follower base gives you instant social proof.

### What an aged Page unlocks

1. **Higher ad trust**, campaigns launch on a stronger footing.
2. **Instant brand credibility**, your presence looks established.
3. **Better organic reach**, more eyes on your content.
4. **Fewer restrictions**, you skip the limits that hit brand-new Pages.

### Pick the right Page

From a clean aged base to a fully verified, monetized Page, there is a tier for every stage:

| Page | What you get | Best for | From |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Aged Reinstated** | Clean aged history | A trusted starting base | $35 |
| **1K to 3K Followers** | Early follower base | First social proof | $45 |
| **5K Followers** | Mid follower base | Stronger credibility | $65 |
| **10K Followers** | Large follower base | An established presence | $110 |
| **Livestream Ads Ready** | Livestream-enabled | Live shopping campaigns | $200 |
| **Monetized (10K)** | Monetization enabled | Earning plus advertising | $300 |
| **Verified (Blue Badge)** | Blue tick + 10K | Maximum authority | $600 |

{% callout variant="tip" title="Which Page should I buy?" %}
Just need a trusted base for ads? Start with an **Aged Reinstated** Page. Building a brand that needs to look big and legit fast? Go for a **Follower** or **Verified** Page. See live prices on our [pricing page](https://goadsagency.com/pricing) or [ask our team](/docs/questions-bank/support).
